    "They effectively addresses the problems associated with inadequate feature representation and inefficient information transfer.",
    "This methodology offers a powerful means for fusing multi-scale feature information, thereby enhancing the model's performance and its ability to generalize.",
    "Focal lossFocal Loss [11], a loss function specifically engineered to mitigate the issue of class imbalance, is particularly effective in tasks related to object detection.",
